{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/NoRulesNoRescueHeader.png?t=1700469062\" /><br>Inescapable: No Rules, No Rescue is a social thriller set in a tropical island resort: you\u2019ve been kidnapped and forced to participate in a twisted reality TV show with 10 strangers. At the end of your stay, you\u2019ll receive $500,000. There\u2019s just one catch\u2014on the island there are no rules, and no hope of rescue.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/WhatShouldWeDoSmall.gif?t=1700469062\" /><br><br>Inescapable: No Rules, No Rescue\u2019s story explores human nature and how far people will go for social clout, wealth, and their own desires\u2014and how much further they might be willing to go when they have permission to ignore the rules.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/UnrestrainedByLawsSmall.gif?t=1700469062\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/KeyFeaturesHeader.png?t=1700469062\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple narrative paths<br></li><li>A provocative character-driven story<br></li><li>A diverse cast of characters with intriguing personalities and backstories<br></li><li>Hours of voice-acted dialogue<br></li><li>A full-length original soundtrack with music from Shinji Hosoe (<i>Zero Escape</i>), and Matias Lehtoranta</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/NoFunnyBusinessSmall.gif?t=1700469062\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/PlayTheDemo.png?t=1700469062\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Game Addict","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/st